  "body": "<code>admin.chainSyncStatus</code> returns the known blockchain  synchronisation status including the number of blocks to be imported, e.g, \n\n<pre>{\n  blocksAvailable: 0,\n  blocksWaitingForImport: 83,\n  estimate: '14m21.854776871s',\n  importing: 38\n}</pre>\n\n\nCurrently go-ethereum does not inform the miners that the blockchain is out of synch leading to a wastage of electricity.\n\nCan a 'pause mining' instruction be implemented across the clients and miners please?\n",
